<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Vote Gold — Assistant Director of Socials | COLAW Caleb University</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;700;900&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --blue: #0A2472;
    --gold: #D4A017;
    --gold-light: #F5C842;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --dark: #060D1F;
    --red: #CC0000;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    background: var(--dark);
    color: var(--white);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ===== NAV ===== */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(6, 13, 31, 0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 14px 40px;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
  }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 30px; }
  .nav-links a {
    color: var(--white); text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold-light); }

  /* ===== HERO ===== */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #060D1F 0%, #0A2472 50%, #060D1F 100%);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding-top: 80px;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 70% 50%, rgba(212,160,23,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 80% at 20% 50%, rgba(10,36,114,0.4) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* diagonal gold stripe */
  .hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 200%;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--gold);
    top: 50%;
    left: -50%;
    transform: rotate(-8deg);
    opacity: 0.15;
  }

  .hero-text {
    padding: 60px 60px 60px 80px;
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    animation: fadeInLeft 0.9s ease forwards;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInLeft {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-40px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 5px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold-light); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow::before {
    content: ''; display: block; width: 40px; height: 2px; background: var(--gold);
  }

  .hero-vote {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.2rem; color: var(--red);
    letter-spacing: 8px;
    text-shadow: 3px 3px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
    color: var(--white);
    text-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--gold), 8px 8px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .hero-name span { color: var(--gold-light); }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--dark);
    padding: 16px 40px;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 3px solid var(--gold);
    transition: all 0.3s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cta-btn::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: var(--blue);
    transform: translateX(-100%);
    transition: transform 0.3s;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .cta-btn:hover::after { transform: translateX(0); }
  .cta-btn:hover { color: var(--gold); }
  .cta-btn span { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  /* hero image */
  .hero-image {
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: flex-end;
    height: 100%;
    animation: fadeInRight 0.9s ease 0.2s forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }
  @keyframes fadeInRight {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(40px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
  }

  .hero-img-wrap {
    position: relative;
    width: 420px;
    max-width: 90%;
  }

  .hero-img-wrap::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -10px; right: -10px;
    width: 100%; height: 85%;
    border: 4px solid var(--gold);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero-img-wrap img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 20px 60px rgba(212,160,23,0.3));
  }

  .badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px; left: -20px;
    width: 90px; height: 90px;
    background: var(--red);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    border: 3px solid white;
    z-index: 2;
    animation: spin-badge 8s linear infinite;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(204,0,0,0.5);
  }
  @keyframes spin-badge {
    0%, 90% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    95% { transform: rotate(10deg); }
    100% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
  }
  .badge-vote {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem; color: white; line-height: 1;
  }
  .badge-star { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--gold-light); }

  /* ===== SECTION SHARED ===== */
  section { padding: 100px 80px; }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 6px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  }
  .section-label::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); opacity: 0.3; }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  /* ===== PROBLEMS ===== */
  .problems-section {
    background: #070E20;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .problems-section::before {
    content: 'PROBLEMS';
    position: absolute;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 20vw;
    color: rgba(204,0,0,0.04);
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    white-space: nowrap;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .problems-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .problem-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(204,0,0,0.3);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--red);
    padding: 36px 28px;
    position: relative;
    transition: transform 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .problem-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    border-color: var(--red);
    background: rgba(204,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .problem-num {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: rgba(204,0,0,0.15);
    line-height: 1;
    position: absolute;
    top: 10px; right: 20px;
  }
  .problem-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .problem-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .problem-card p {
    font-size: 0.88rem; line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  }

  /* ===== SOLUTIONS ===== */
  .solutions-section {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0A2472 0%, #060D1F 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .solutions-section::before {
    content: 'SOLUTIONS';
    position: absolute;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18vw;
    color: rgba(212,160,23,0.05);
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    white-space: nowrap;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .solutions-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .solutions-img-wrap {
    position: relative;
  }
  .solutions-img-wrap::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: -12px;
    border: 3px solid var(--gold);
    transform: rotate(2deg);
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .solutions-img-wrap img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 20px 50px rgba(212,160,23,0.25));
  }

  .solutions-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }

  .solution-item {
    display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 24px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212,160,23,0.2);
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .solution-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: 4px;
    background: var(--gold);
  }
  .solution-item:hover {
    background: rgba(212,160,23,0.08);
    transform: translateX(6px);
  }
  .solution-check {
    width: 44px; height: 44px; flex-shrink: 0;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--dark);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 900;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .solution-item h3 {
    font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--gold-light); margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .solution-item p {
    font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
  }

  /* ===== WHY GOLD BANNER ===== */
  .why-section {
    background: var(--gold);
    padding: 80px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .why-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      45deg,
      transparent,
      transparent 20px,
      rgba(0,0,0,0.04) 20px,
      rgba(0,0,0,0.04) 40px
    );
  }
  .why-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    color: var(--dark);
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .why-section p {
    font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(6,13,31,0.8);
    max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ===== FOOTER ===== */
  footer {
    background: #030710;
    border-top: 3px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 50px 80px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .footer-name {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 3rem; color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .footer-sub {
    font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  }

  /* ===== TICKER ===== */
  .ticker {
    background: var(--red);
    padding: 12px 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .ticker-inner {
    display: inline-flex;
    animation: ticker 20s linear infinite;
    gap: 60px;
  }
  @keyframes ticker {
    from { transform: translateX(0); }
    to   { transform: translateX(-50%); }
  }
  .ticker-item {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: white;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .ticker-sep { color: var(--gold-light); }

  /* ===== SCROLL ANIMATIONS ===== */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 100px 30px 40px; }
    .hero-text { padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
    .hero-eyebrow { justify-content: center; }
    .hero-image { padding: 20px; }
    .hero-img-wrap { width: 280px; }
    section { padding: 60px 30px; }
    .solutions-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .solutions-img-wrap { display: none; }
    nav { padding: 14px 20px; }
    .nav-links { gap: 16px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">GOLD 2025</div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#hero">Home</a>
    <a href="#problems">Problems</a>
    <a href="#solutions">Solutions</a>
    <a href="#why">Why Gold</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- TICKER -->
<div class="ticker" style="margin-top:0; position:relative; z-index:99; margin-top:62px;">
  <div class="ticker-inner">
    <span class="ticker-item">VOTE ASHIMOLOWO GOLD</span>
    <span class="ticker-sep">✦</span>
    <span class="ticker-item">ASSISTANT DIRECTOR OF SOCIALS</span>
    <span class="ticker-sep">✦</span>
    <span class="ticker-item">NOT JUST EVENTS — A BETTER COLAW</span>
    <span class="ticker-sep">✦</span>
    <span class="ticker-item">COLLEGE OF LAW · CALEB UNIVERSITY</span>
    <span class="ticker-sep">✦</span>
    <span class="ticker-item">VOTE ASHIMOLOWO GOLD</span>
    <span class="ticker-sep">✦</span>
    <span class="ticker-item">ASSISTANT DIRECTOR OF SOCIALS</span>
    <span class="ticker-sep">✦</span>
    <span class="ticker-item">NOT JUST EVENTS — A BETTER COLAW</span>
    <span class="ticker-sep">✦</span>
    <span class="ticker-item">COLLEGE OF LAW · CALEB UNIVERSITY</span>
    <span class="ticker-sep">✦</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" id="hero">
  <div class="hero-text">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">College of Law · Caleb University · Lagos</div>
    <div class="hero-vote">✦ VOTE ✦</div>
    <h1 class="hero-name">ASHIMOLOWO<br><span>GOLD</span></h1>
    <div class="hero-title">For Assistant Director of Socials</div>
    <p class="hero-tagline">"Student life is not complete<br>without social life — let me bring<br>the experience to you."</p>
    <a href="#solutions" class="cta-btn"><span>See My Vision →</span></a>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-image">
    <div class="hero-img-wrap">
      <div class="badge">
        <span class="badge-star">★★★</span>
        <span class="badge-vote">VOTE</span>
        <span class="badge-vote">GOLD</span>
        <span class="badge-star">★★★</span>
      </div>
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Ashimolowo Gold" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PROBLEMS -->
<section class="problems-section" id="problems">
  <div class="section-label">The Reality We Face</div>
  <h2 class="section-title" style="color: #FF4444;">THE <span style="color:white">PROBLEMS</span><br>IN COLAW</h2>
  <div class="problems-grid">
    <div class="problem-card reveal">
      <div class="problem-num">01</div>
      <div class="problem-icon">😔</div>
      <h3>Social Isolation & Burnout</h3>
      <p>Law students are buried under intense academic pressure with little to no organized social outlets, leading to burnout, anxiety, and disconnection from peers.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-card reveal">
      <div class="problem-num">02</div>
      <div class="problem-icon">🏚️</div>
      <h3>Weak Class Community</h3>
      <p>There is a lack of bonding activities across levels. Students from different years rarely interact, creating a fragmented and divided student body in COLAW.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-card reveal">
      <div class="problem-num">03</div>
      <div class="problem-icon">📅</div>
      <h3>Poor Event Planning & Execution</h3>
      <p>Past social events have been poorly organized, under-publicized, and poorly attended. Students feel events don't reflect their interests or celebrate their identity as law students.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-card reveal">
      <div class="problem-num">04</div>
      <div class="problem-icon">🤝</div>
      <h3>Lack of Networking Opportunities</h3>
      <p>There are virtually no structured opportunities for law students to build professional networks, connect with alumni, or engage with legal professionals during their time on campus.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-card reveal">
      <div class="problem-num">05</div>
      <div class="problem-icon">🎓</div>
      <h3>No Culture of Celebration</h3>
      <p>Academic milestones, birthdays, and student achievements go unrecognized. COLAW lacks a culture of celebrating its students and honouring their progress and excellence.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-card reveal">
      <div class="problem-num">06</div>
      <div class="problem-icon">📢</div>
      <h3>Student Voice Not Heard</h3>
      <p>Students rarely have input into the social agenda. Events are planned without consulting the student body, leaving the majority unrepresented and disengaged.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SOLUTIONS -->
<section class="solutions-section" id="solutions">
  <div class="section-label">Gold's Blueprint</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">MY <span style="color: var(--gold-light);">SOLUTIONS</span><br>FOR COLAW</h2>
  <div class="solutions-layout">
    <div class="solutions-img-wrap reveal">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Vote Gold — Campaign Poster" />
    </div>
    <div class="solutions-list">
      <div class="solution-item reveal">
        <div class="solution-check">✓</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Monthly COLAW Social Events</h3>
          <p>Structured, consistent monthly events — game nights, dinner socials, themed hangouts — designed to decompress law students and build real friendships across levels.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="solution-item reveal">
        <div class="solution-check">✓</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Cross-Level Bonding Programs</h3>
          <p>Organized mixers and mentorship activities that connect 100-level students with finalists, building a strong, unified COLAW family and a lasting sense of belonging.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="solution-item reveal">
        <div class="solution-check">✓</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Law Networking Nights</h3>
          <p>Termly events that bring in COLAW alumni, legal practitioners, and professionals to help students build career connections while still in school.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="solution-item reveal">
        <div class="solution-check">✓</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Student-Led Event Planning</h3>
          <p>A transparent event committee where students submit ideas and vote on social activities — ensuring every event truly reflects what COLAW students want.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="solution-item reveal">
        <div class="solution-check">✓</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Culture of Recognition & Celebration</h3>
          <p>A dedicated program to celebrate academic wins, birthdays, and milestones — making every COLAW student feel seen, valued, and proud of their community.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHY GOLD BANNER -->
<div class="why-section" id="why">
  <h2>WHY CHOOSE GOLD?</h2>
  <p>Because COLAW deserves more than ordinary events. It deserves a social director who is passionate, organized, and truly invested in making every student's experience unforgettable. Gold is not just a name — it's a standard.</p>
</div>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer>
  <div class="footer-name">ASHIMOLOWO GOLD</div>
  <div class="footer-sub">Assistant Director of Socials · College of Law · Caleb University · Lagos, Nigeria</div>
  <div style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); letter-spacing: 2px;">NOT JUST EVENTS. A BETTER COLAW. ✦</div>
</footer>

<script>
  // Scroll reveal
  const reveals = document.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach((entry, i) => {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) {
        setTimeout(() => entry.target.classList.add('visible'), i * 80);
      }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.1 });
  reveals.forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
</script>
</body>
</html>
